==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Whinny
<hw>Whin"ny</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Abounding in whin, gorse, or
furze.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A fine, large, <qex>whinny</qex>, . . . unimproved common.</q>
<rj><qau>Sterne.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
